attributes.title: Absolutely awful
attributes.review:
At first I thought that this app would be good for the White House but judging by the absolute disaster that this app is, I am convinced that maybe we need someone with more experience than a reality tv personality who was an utter failure at business living off his dad’s money and bankrupting every business he touches running the country. 

I thought that this app might help with finding a hot wife too but then I realized that she would never actually love me she is just in it for the money and all the app could ever possibly be good for would be having to pay women to pretend to like me for a few brief moments that I’d have to pay my lawyer to cover up later, or even worse, all of the accusations of unwanted sexual assault. 

 It’s just absolutely the worst app ever for dealing with healthcare or education or the economy or basically any other necessary function of an app like this. Pretty much the worst app ever created in our country’s 243 year history.

attributes.title: Big no no for me
attributes.review: I very excited too have and app where all my fellow trump supporters could go but as soon as I opened the app I was met with constant glitches as I was putting in my information. At the beginning the things I was filling out were completely normal but the questions started to get a bit more personal, it asked for my address, social security number and my bra size . After I put all my information in my phone screen started to flash and my phone completely shut down , it took me  a hole 24 HOURS to get my phone working again . Im very disappointed with this app 😡😡
